------------------------
OBJECTIVE
-------------------------

  Load zfishbook (Ekker Lab) data into ZFIN.
  Make attributions to these data.

-------------------------
EXECUTION
--------------------------

   Run:	./zfishbook.sh

   Triggered manually via the Jenkins job Zfishbook-Data-Load, but that job
   has not run since 2019 (build #3) -- this load appears dormant.


